<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VirtuLearn Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dyjhsyblr/image/upload/v1725297294/Designer_bgyrub.png" alt="VirtuLearn Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
            <p>Hi <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for signing up with VirtuLearn! To complete your registration, please use the following activation code:</p>
            <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
            <p>If you did not create an account, no further action is required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 VirtuLearn. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
